Invocation Name: distance calculator
des:
Distance Calculator tells you the distance between any two place and the time taken to travel by car.

Using state of the art location parsing, we determine accurate locations and provide real time travel duration reporting.

Try saying,

Alexa, Ask Distance Calculator distance between San Francisco and Portland

Alexa, Ask Distance Calculator distance between Eiffel Tower and Big Ben

Alexa, Ask Distance Calculator distance between Los Angeles and San Francisco

Alexa, Ask Distance Calculator distance between Stanford and Golden Gate Park
